#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:2
msgid "S3"
msgstr "S3"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:4
msgid ""
"An L2 adapter that stores KV cache objects as S3 objects using the AWS "
"Common Runtime (CRT).  Works with AWS S3, S3 Express One Zone, and any "
"S3-compatible endpoint (MinIO, Ceph RGW, etc.)."
msgstr "一个 L2 适配器，使用 AWS 通用运行时 (CRT) 将 KV cache 对象存储为 S3 对象。支持 AWS S3、S3 Express One Zone 以及任何兼容 S3 的端点（MinIO、Ceph RGW 等）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:8
msgid "**Required fields:**"
msgstr "**必填字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:10
msgid ""
"``s3_endpoint``: Bucket URL -- either ``\"s3://<bucket>\"`` or the bare "
"host form (used for non-AWS endpoints)."
msgstr "``s3_endpoint``: 存储桶 URL -- 可以是 ``\"s3://<bucket>\"`` 或纯主机名形式（用于非 AWS 端点）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:12
msgid "``s3_region``: AWS region string (e.g. ``\"us-west-2\"``)."
msgstr "``s3_region``: AWS 区域字符串（例如 ``\"us-west-2\"``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:14
msgid "**Optional fields:**"
msgstr "**可选字段：**"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:16
msgid "``s3_num_io_threads`` (int, default ``64``): Number of CRT I/O threads."
msgstr "``s3_num_io_threads`` (int, default ``64``): CRT I/O 线程数。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:17
msgid "``s3_prefer_http2`` (bool, default ``true``): Negotiate HTTP/2 via ALPN."
msgstr "``s3_prefer_http2`` (bool, default ``true``): 通过 ALPN 协商 HTTP/2。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:18
msgid ""
"``s3_enable_s3express`` (bool, default ``false``): Enable S3 Express "
"signing for S3 Express One Zone buckets."
msgstr "``s3_enable_s3express`` (bool, default ``false``): 为 S3 Express 单可用区存储桶启用 S3 Express 签名。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:20
msgid ""
"``disable_tls`` (bool, default ``false``): Bypass TLS when pointing at a "
"plain-HTTP endpoint (e.g. a local MinIO)."
msgstr "``disable_tls`` (bool, default ``false``): 在指向普通 HTTP 端点时绕过 TLS（例如本地 MinIO）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:22
msgid ""
"``aws_access_key_id`` / ``aws_secret_access_key`` (string): Static "
"credentials; omit both to use the AWS default credential provider chain "
"(environment, EC2 instance profile, etc.)."
msgstr "``aws_access_key_id`` / ``aws_secret_access_key`` （字符串）：静态凭证；若两者均省略，则使用 AWS 默认凭证提供链（环境变量、EC2 实例配置等）。"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/s3.rst:25
msgid ""
"``max_capacity_gb`` (float, default ``0.0``): Aggregate capacity used by "
"``get_usage()``.  A value of ``0`` disables aggregate eviction "
"(``usage_fraction == -1.0``)."
msgstr "``max_capacity_gb`` (浮点数，默认 ``0.0``)：由 ``get_usage()`` 使用的总容量。值为 ``0`` 时禁用总逐出（``usage_fraction == -1.0``）。"

